2023-07-04

The current scanpypi does not handle the newer pyproject.toml format
for Python package configuation. There is a patch that adds most of the
functionality here:

https://patchwork.ozlabs.org/project/buildroot/patch/20220818082617.24624-1-james.hilliard1@gmail.com/

But it does not handle setuptools based builds and dependencies. Included
here is a complete scanpypi that does so.
